Author: zhuazhuanownow
Text: when i first started college i developed pretty bad agoraphobia on top of anxiety i already had, and was too scared to use the student kitchen in case someone else came in, and also too scared to go out and buy prepackaged food - lost like 10kg/20lbs over the first semester. Truly, it was the best of times, it was the worst of times (: (:
